Maintainer: Kirk Li <cocokecoli@gmail.com>
Description: PCRA is a companion package to the text Robust Portfolio Construction 
  and Risk Analysis authored by R. Douglas Martin, Thomas K. Philips, Bernd Scherer,
  Stoyan Stoyanov and Kirk Li, to be published by Springer in 2023. The package includes
  cross-sections of data for approximately 300 stocks from the Center for Research on
  Security Prices, LLC (CRSP), and 14 corresponding factor exposures from S&P Global.
  The book covers classical and modern robust methods of portfolio construction and
  risk analysis with a reproducibality focus.  The data and function in the package  
  support this focus. Extensive R scripts based on package functions for each chapter
  reproduce most of the tables and figures in the chapter.  
